'''Jedi Mind Juice''' was a popular term for the green ichor secreted by a scared [[cochlera]]. It was believed that the substance would grant one resistance to [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Mind trick/Legends|mind tricks]], though it had not been conclusively proven.

